        <p>The plant adoption process involves filling out an adopter's form. Once the form is processed and approved, we will contact you either through a phone call or via email.</p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary page-button" type="button">
            <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="AdoptersForm" asp-action="create"> Click Here</a>

        </button>
    </div>
